{"tid":8293,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得拍拖呢種關係好虛無","createTime":"2016-11-28T09:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T09:30:50.000Z","uid":2786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74c0eb849ad11c2a8d4e254a313c8cc51852b359","tid":8293,"uid":2786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:24:40.000Z","msg":"無論當初你地點樣山盟海誓<br />\n叫晒對方老公老婆 當大家係最親密既人<br />\n有幾多快樂美好既回憶 經歷過幾多都好<br />\n<br />\n幾個月 甚至幾年既感情 都可以因爲一d野<br />\n可能係人 可能係小事 可能係環境既轉變<br />\n而毀於一旦 乜都無晒 得返一堆回憶<br />\n一諗到呢到就咩信心都無晒 <br />\n<br />\n如果唔可以行到最後 <br />\n到底係為咩同人拍拖 為人付出？"},{"pid":"21e7fe1525f3c6b59532cfc9a73b377c1b3cffdc","tid":8293,"uid":27636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"但係你唔試下去同人拍拖，你點會知邊個會係你終身伴侶。"},{"pid":"006a244d850045c6ad0533f76b43d6718d454110","tid":8293,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:33:56.000Z","msg":"其實結左婚都一樣好虛無，<br />\n完全睇雙方點維繫<br />\n<br />\n唔係結左婚等於畢業，<br />\n婚後先係真正挑戰"},{"pid":"79d137c65576173edbd3400a11f8e20fa99f04d2","tid":8293,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:34:44.000Z","msg":"Long d左8個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍拖對我嚟講只不過係精神上嘅交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8216e4536d811c91ba3a2cf7f7faffb5f21645","tid":8293,"uid":31567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:39:45.000Z","msg":"當初講到有幾愛 最後一句淡左就乜都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dbeb1023ae2c721bec3cb0bdaa33d4a5b57e69","tid":8293,"uid":29520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:43:55.000Z","msg":"所有承諾都係假 幾多年感情都冇用 一出現第三者真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe145c2ee89f7b3d83400442d368b66ead3ef6cd","tid":8293,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:45:12.000Z","msg":"做人都好虛無啊，咁你又做"},{"pid":"72f83c887a1400e27fd13cecefc34474fd1a04b6","tid":8293,"uid":3671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"係啊 係咁嫁咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e3c58717569ca973a23c615797ecbec8665856","tid":8293,"uid":2786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做人都好虛無啊，咁你又做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n說話又唔好咁講 呀媽生我落黎 我無得揀"},{"pid":"06a7318da08a02ff522bdfe7b4e951b50a58ebe4","tid":8293,"uid":2786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所有承諾都係假 幾多年感情都冇用 一出現第三者真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算對方肯返返黎 大家都有條刺"},{"pid":"35da9e128441ad8800ebf1c7a2f898e9b7831991","tid":8293,"uid":22952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所有承諾都係假 幾多年感情都冇用 一出現第三者真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算對方肯返返黎 大家都有條刺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n情愛就似垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src